  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Max Ranks</strong>: 5</p><hr /><p>A Weakened creature is unable to exert their maximum physicality and effort as they have had the wind blown out of them.</p><ul><li><p>A <strong>Weakened</strong> creature reduces damage it deals with attacks and Jutsu by -4 for each rank it has.</p></li><li><p>A <strong>Weakened</strong> creature has a -1 penalty to Strength saving throws.</p></li><li><p>The <strong>Weakened</strong> condition last for the duration of its duration or 1 minute has passed, whichever comes first.</p></li></ul>",
